<p align="center"><strong><span style="text-decoration: underline;">English Translation</span></strong></p>
<p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: small;">This decad  of sweet songs by Kulasekaran, Lord of Kolli city and King of Kudal,  Madurai, on the laments of young cowherd dames desirous of blending with  the Lord of lotus-dame-Lakshmi in the dead of the night, -- those who  master it shall suffer no misery.</span></p></div><span class="article_separator">&nbsp;</span>
